===Noun===
'''computer virus''' (''plural'' '''computer viruses''' ''or'' '''computer virii''' (''non-standard''))

(''computing'') A [[program]] transmitted between computers via networks, especially the Internet (or, formerly, via [[floppy disk]]s), without the knowledge or consent of the recipient, that usually causes wilful damage to data and is able to [[replicate]] itself and send copies to further computers on the network.

